concept-thats-failed/0000018b-6ce7-db57-a7cb-ecff6ae90000</guid></item><item><title>“当他呼唤妈妈和爸爸但他们没有来时，我们该怎么说？”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-26/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/what-are-we-supposed-to-say-when-he-calls-for-mommy-and-daddy-and-they-dont-come/0000018b-6c9a-de3d-abdb-7ffa00610000</link><description>他的母亲被哈马斯杀害。他的父亲被扣为人质。 2 岁的阿尔莫格·利维 (Almog Levy) 是黑色星期六失去父母的 21 名以色列孩子之一</description><pubDate>Thu, 26 Oct 2023 17:14:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-26/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/what-are-we-supposed-to-say-when-he-calls-for-mommy-and-daddy-and-they-dont-come/0000018b-6c9a-de3d-abdb-7ffa00610000</guid></item><item><title>在战争的掩护下，以色列试图推迟公众信息自由的请求</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-26/ty-article/.premium/under-cover-of-war-israel-seeks-to-deny-public-freedom-of-information-requests/0000018b-6c5a-de3d-abdb-7f7a59250000</link><description>司法部备忘录将允许以色列公共当局将响应信息自由请求的时间推迟至少七个月，据称是由于战争。反对党议员梅拉夫·本-阿里表示，“不会允许在战争的支持下进行反民主劫持”</description><pubDate>Thu, 26 Oct 2023 16:47:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-26/ty-article/.premium/under-cover-of-war-israel-seeks-to-deny-public-freedom-of-information-requests/0000018b-6c5a-de3d-abdb-7f7a59250000</guid></item><item><title>如果以色列推翻加沙的哈马斯会发生什么</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-26/ty-article-magazine/.premium/what-happens-if-israel-topples-hamas-in-gaza/0000018b-6c66-d90b-a7df-7e6675600000</link><description>如今，以色列对于加沙地带的未来有四种选择。所有这些都很糟糕，其中有两个简直是灾难性的</description><pubDate>Thu, 26 Oct 2023 15:25:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-26/ty-article-magazine/.premium/what-happens-if-israel-topples-hamas-in-gaza/0000018b-6c66-d90b-a7df-7e6675600000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队发言人成为加沙对抗哈马斯战争的代言人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-26/ty-article/.premium/israels-army-spokesperson-has-become-the-face-of-the-war-against-hamas-in-gaza/0000018b-6b87-d14c-adfb-ef9f280f0000</link><description>双桅船。丹尼尔·哈加里将军与军队决策者关系密切，拥有丰富的作战经验，在公共外交危机中每天都会向心烦意乱的以色列公众发表讲话</description><pubDate>Thu, 26 Oct 2023 14:54:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-26/ty-article/.premium/israels-army-spokesperson-has-become-the-face-of-the-war-against-hamas-in-gaza/0000018b-6b87-d14c-adfb-ef9f280f0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队连夜入侵加沙，瞄准哈马斯恐怖分子和基础设施</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-26/ty-article/.premium/israeli-forces-targeted-hamas-terrorists-infrastructure-during-incursion-into-gaza/0000018b-6c03-db57-a7cb-ec9f03cb0000</link><description>军方消息人士称，此次行动比之前的行动更加深入，是为下一阶段的战斗做准备，特别是对加沙的全面地面入侵。</description><pubDate>Thu, 26 Oct 2023 14:36:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-26/ty-article/.premium/israeli-forces-targeted-hamas-terrorists-infrastructure-during-incursion-into-gaza/0000018b-6c03-db57-a7cb-ec9f03cb0000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯袭击后身为加州的以色列人：现在我知道“进步的巨魔”是什么样子了</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-26/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israeli-in-the-u-s-after-hamas-attack-now-i-know-what-progressive-trolls-are-like/0000018b-6ba1-db57-a7cb-ebbfba210000</link><description>哈马斯大屠杀发生时，以色列裔加拿大诗人玛雅·特维特·达扬正在圣地亚哥一所大学任教。她在这里写下了她在校园的经历以及自由派美国人的无情回应</description><pubDate>Thu, 26 Oct 2023 12:53:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-26/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israeli-in-the-u-s-after-hamas-attack-now-i-know-what-progressive-trolls-are-like/0000018b-6ba1-db57-a7cb-ebbfba210000</guid></item><item><title>“令人不安”：以色列特使在外交失望之际猛烈抨击中国对哈马斯袭击的反应</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-26/ty-article/.premium/disturbing-israeli-envoy-slams-chinas-response-to-hamas-attack-amid-diplomatic-letdown/0000018b-6ba5-db57-a7cb-ebbf82ce0000</link><description>中国谴责冲突中的暴力和针对平民的袭击，虽然中国外交部长王毅宣称以色列的行动“超出自卫范围”，但他在评论中没有点名哈马斯</description><pubDate>Thu, 26 Oct 2023 12:12:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-26/ty-article/.premium/disturbing-israeli-envoy-slams-chinas-response-to-hamas-attack-amid-diplomatic-letdown/0000018b-6ba5-db57-a7cb-ebbf82ce0000</guid></item><item><title>面对日益高涨的反犹太主义，澳大利亚犹太人的“妄想”早已不复存在</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/news/2023-10-26/ty-article/.premium/the-delusions-of-australias-jews-are-long-gone-in-the-face-of-rising-antisemitism/0000018b-6b81-d14c-adfb-ef998c1e0000</link><description>自10月7日以来的几周内，澳大利亚反犹太事件有所增加，促使政府增加对犹太社区的安全资金</description><pubDate>Thu, 26 Oct 2023 11:53:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/news/2023-10-26/ty-article/.premium/the-delusions-of-australias-jews-are-long-gone-in-the-face-of-rising-antisemitism/0000018b-6b81-d14c-adfb-ef998c1e0000</guid></item><item><title>纽约以色列艺术家的讽刺视频被亲巴勒斯坦人歪曲后受到威胁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-26/ty-article/.premium/israeli-ny-based-artist-threatened-after-her-video-is-distorted-by-pro-palestinians/0000018b-6b2e-de3d-abdb-7f7e36e80000</link><description>一位视频和表演艺术家上传了一段视频，嘲笑美国学者在以色列哈马斯大屠杀问题上的虚伪。亲巴勒斯坦活动人士重新编辑了它，引发了一系列辱骂和威胁</description><pubDate>Thu, 26 Oct 2023 11:42:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-26/ty-article/.premium/israeli-ny-based-artist-threatened-after-her-video-is-distorted-by-pro-palestinians/0000018b-6b2e-de3d-abdb-7f7e36e80000</guid></item><item><title>在美国校园里，进步左派揭示了其对哈马斯和以色列人的道德堕落</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-26/ty-article-opinion/.premium/on-u-s-campuses-the-progressive-left-reveals-its-moral-degradation/0000018b-6b2d-de3d-abdb-7f7d27810000</link><description>简单化的意识形态棱镜，加上不断需要站在历史的“正确一边”，扭曲了有关哈马斯袭击以色列的基本事实和道德——这种不雅行为正在席卷美国校园</description><pubDate>Thu, 26 Oct 2023 11:03:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-26/ty-article-opinion/.premium/on-u-s-campuses-the-progressive-left-reveals-its-moral-degradation/0000018b-6b2d-de3d-abdb-7f7d27810000</guid></item><item><title>以色列基布兹的早期历史，早在哈马斯袭击之前</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-26/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israeli-kibbutzs-early-days-long-before-hamas-attack/0000018b-6b70-db57-a7cb-ebffc30b0000</link><description>纳哈尔奥兹是本月早些时候被哈马斯摧毁的加沙地区众多社区之一。维尔纳·布劳恩 (Werner Braun) 1956 年拍摄的照片展现了基布兹从贫瘠土地崛起的令人振奋的场景</description><pubDate>Thu, 26 Oct 2023 10:52:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-26/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israeli-kibbutzs-early-days-long-before-hamas-attack/0000018b-6b70-db57-a7cb-ebffc30b0000</guid></item><item><title>巴勒斯坦人和他们的西方盟友如何为哈马斯的恐怖行为辩护</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-26/ty-article-opinion/.highlight/how-palestinians-and-their-western-allies-justify-the-horrors-committed-by-hamas/0000018b-6b34-d14c-adfb-efbcb9280000</link><description></description><pubDate>Thu, 26 Oct 2023 10:00:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-26/ty-article-opinion/.highlight/how-palestinians-and-their-western-allies-justify-the-horrors-committed-by-hamas/0000018b-6b34-d14c-adfb-efbcb9280000</guid></item><item><title>以色列谴责俄罗斯接待哈马斯代表团；以色列国防军在加沙炮火中打死数名指挥官</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-26/ty-article-live/idf-intercepts-rocket-shot-from-lebanon-putin-conflict-may-spill-over-beyond-middle-east/0000018b-69d2-d979-a3bb-ebf7c9c20000</link><description>以色列国防军在加沙地带北部进行夜间装甲袭击 ■ 军方称，过去一天袭击了 250 多个哈马斯目标 ■ 以色列国防军隔夜拦截一枚来自黎巴嫩的地对空导弹，空军瞄准发射源 ■ 美国将向以色列运送全部铁穹库存■ 消息人士称，释放大量人质的谈判正在进行中，可能会在几天内完成 ■ 自 10 月 7 日以来，哈马斯至少造成 1,300 人死亡 ■ 哈马斯管理的卫生部：超过 6,000 名加沙人被杀，约 17,000 人受伤</description><pubDate>Thu, 26 Oct 2023 09:47:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-26/ty-article-live/idf-intercepts-rocket-shot-from-lebanon-putin-conflict-may-spill-over-beyond-middle-east/0000018b-69d2-d979-a3bb-ebf7c9c20000</guid></item><item><title>法国马克龙寻求国际支持其建立反哈马斯联盟的提议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-26/ty-article/frances-macron-seeks-support-for-his-proposal-to-build-a-coalition-against-hamas/0000018b-6aec-df4c-a78b-7eedf2bc0000</link><description>为了进一步建立反伊斯兰国联盟，马克龙会见了以色列、约旦河西岸、约旦和埃及的领导人，但他们都没有公开谈论这个问题。美国官员称阿拉伯国家没有兴趣建立这样一支部队</description><pubDate>Thu, 26 Oct 2023 08:58:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-26/ty-article/frances-macron-seeks-support-for-his-proposal-to-build-a-coalition-against-hamas/0000018b-6aec-df4c-a78b-7eedf2bc0000</guid></item><item><title>加沙工人描述了战争爆发以来以色列拘留中心的不人道待遇</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-26/ty-article/.premium/gazan-workers-describe-inhuman-treatment-at-israeli-detention-facilities-since-war-started/0000018b-6631-d473-a5fb-66f9fa930000</link><description>一名从拘留所获释的巴勒斯坦人表示，工人们被关在过度拥挤的“笼子状”围栏内，戴着手铐，蒙住眼睛，并被拒绝会见律师或红十字会代表。人权组织称，以色列已经失踪了数千名加沙合法工人</description><pubDate>Thu, 26 Oct 2023 08:49:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-26/ty-article/.premium/gazan-workers-describe-inhuman-treatment-at-israeli-detention-facilities-since-war-started/0000018b-6631-d473-a5fb-66f9fa930000</guid></item><item><title>以色列警方警告会场所有者“后果”后，阿拉伯犹太人会议被取消</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-26/ty-article/.premium/arab-jewish-conference-canceled-after-israel-police-warn-venue-owner-of-consequences/0000018b-6ad2-db57-a7cb-eadfb5700000</link><description>被取消的会议旨在呼吁立即结束战争并将平民从暴力循环中解救出来。警方指责这一事件煽动针对以色列，阿拉伯-以色列领导人称其为“针对阿拉伯公民的政治围困”</description><pubDate>Thu, 26 Oct 2023 08:32:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-26/ty-article/.premium/arab-jewish-conference-canceled-after-israel-police-warn-venue-owner-of-consequences/0000018b-6ad2-db57-a7cb-eadfb5700000</guid></item><item><title>以色列收集针对哈马斯战争罪案件的数字证据</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-10-26/ty-article/.premium/israel-collecting-digital-evidence-for-war-crimes-case-against-hamas/0000018b-6ab1-d326-a39b-6eb99b2f0000</link><description>“图书馆”根据 GoPro 摄像机、社交媒体和在线资源中的视频，识别了哈马斯恐怖分子的身份，并记录了他们如何谋杀 1000 名平民并绑架数百人进入加沙</description><pubDate>Thu, 26 Oct 2023 07:03:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-10-26/ty-article/.premium/israel-collecting-digital-evidence-for-war-crimes-case-against-hamas/0000018b-6ab1-d326-a39b-6eb99b2f0000</guid></item></channel></rss>